\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/MotorsMounted-300x232.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/MotorsMounted-150x116.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/MotorsMounted-768x593.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 384px) 100vw, 384px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Now attach the <strong>Swivel Wheel<\/strong> with two or four <strong>8-32<\/strong> screws as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/SwivelWheelMounted.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/SwivelWheelMounted.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4226\" width=\"385\" height=\"215\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/SwivelWheelMounted.jpg 819w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/SwivelWheelMounted-300x167.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/SwivelWheelMounted-150x84.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/SwivelWheelMounted-768x429.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 385px) 100vw, 385px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Now mount the <strong>IR Sensor<\/strong> using a <strong>2-28<\/strong> screw as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/SensorMounted.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/SensorMounted.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4229\" width=\"397\" height=\"219\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/SensorMounted.jpg 819w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/SensorMounted-300x166.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/SensorMounted-150x83.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/SensorMounted-768x424.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 397px) 100vw, 397px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Now attach the <strong>Motor Controller<\/strong> and <strong>Raspberry Pi<\/strong> mounts with 8-32 screws as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Motor-PiMount.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Motor-PiMount.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4232\" width=\"407\" height=\"276\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Motor-PiMount.jpg 819w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Motor-PiMount-300x203.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Motor-PiMount-150x102.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Motor-PiMount-768x520.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 407px) 100vw, 407px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Now mount the <strong>Motor Controller<\/strong> and Raspberry Pi Zero with 2-28 screws as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/MotorControllerPiMounted.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/MotorControllerPiMounted.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4235\" width=\"415\" height=\"275\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/MotorControllerPiMounted.jpg 819w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/MotorControllerPiMounted-300x199.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/MotorControllerPiMounted-150x99.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/MotorControllerPiMounted-768x509.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 415px) 100vw, 415px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Now mount the Microcontroller Board as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/MicrocontrollerBoard-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/MicrocontrollerBoard-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4237\" width=\"424\" height=\"296\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/MicrocontrollerBoard-1.jpg 780w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/MicrocontrollerBoard-1-300x210.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/MicrocontrollerBoard-1-150x105.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/MicrocontrollerBoard-1-768x537.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 424px) 100vw, 424px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Now insert the <strong>Blue Pill Microcontroller<\/strong> into the socket as shown. Pay close attention to the orientation. If you plug this in backwards it <strong>WILL destroy the device<\/strong> (don&#8217;t ask me how I know this).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/BluePill-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/BluePill-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4240\" width=\"421\" height=\"287\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/BluePill-1.jpg 819w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/BluePill-1-300x204.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/BluePill-1-150x102.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/BluePill-1-768x523.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 421px) 100vw, 421px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Now attach the <strong>Battery Holder<\/strong> using <strong>8-32<\/strong> screws as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/BatteryHolder.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src